{"tid":1544420,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"完了，香港特務機關","createTime":"2019-09-05T14:25:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-05T14:41:16.000Z","uid":230382,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"654d073dc52a6245561efb0cb041e2a738a4d20d","tid":1544420,"uid":230382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T14:25:17.000Z","msg":"他又指，政府可引用《公安條例》，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">由特首授權委任一些處理特別事務的人士當「特務警察」</span></span>，增加檢控或文書工作的人手。他說，條文沒有列明一定只能委任本地人，但他看不到有任何工作適宜內地人士去做。<br />\n<br />\n湯家驊表示，若林鄭現時辭職，比前特首董建華當年離任，留下的後遺症會更大。<br />\n<br />\n湯家驊稱，特首請辭確實需要作不同考慮，亦看不到目前有更好的繼任人選。<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">他認為，林鄭上任後確有成績，對方應留任處理現時問題。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n湯家驊又提到，示威者要求的五大訴求，部分可作討論，<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">但難以做到「缺一不可」</span></span>，強調現階段最重要令社會有和解氣氛，此舉需要各方合作，並非政府一方能塑造出來。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢個仆街真係唯恐天下不亂<br />\n啱啱搞掂一項訴求，又搞啲咁既野，<br />\n佢究竟幾時死？<br />\n<br />\nSource : <a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E6%94%BF%E6%83%85/371272/%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B-%E6%B9%AF%E5%AE%B6%E9%A9%8A-%E5%BC%95-%E7%B7%8A%E6%80%A5%E6%B3%95-%E6%9C%89%E4%BF%9D%E7%95%99-%E7%89%B9%E9%A6%96%E5%8F%AF%E5%A7%94-%E7%89%B9%E5%8B%99%E8%AD%A6%E5%AF%9F\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E6%2594%25BF%25E6%2583%2585%2F371272%2F%25E9%2580%2583%25E7%258A%25AF%25E6%25A2%259D%25E4%25BE%258B-%25E6%25B9%25AF%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E9%25A9%258A-%25E5%25BC%2595-%25E7%25B7%258A%25E6%2580%25A5%25E6%25B3%2595-%25E6%259C%2589%25E4%25BF%259D%25E7%2595%2599-%25E7%2589%25B9%25E9%25A6%2596%25E5%258F%25AF%25E5%25A7%2594-%25E7%2589%25B9%25E5%258B%2599%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%25AF%259F&d=t4s0zgtGzRvDs5iH%2BzYNWAy1DEY80m5I9K8mtjxpzv8%3D&h=c7dba5ca\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E6%94%BF%E6%83%85/371272/%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B-%E6%B9%AF%E5%AE%B6%E9%A9%8A-%E5%BC%95-%E7%B7%8A%E6%80%A5%E6%B3%95-%E6%9C%89%E4%BF%9D%E7%95%99-%E7%89%B9%E9%A6%96%E5%8F%AF%E5%A7%94-%E7%89%B9%E5%8B%99%E8%AD%A6%E5%AF%9F</a>"},{"pid":"cf7f1831ce16581aaa0f9a05eb1f8652e662529f","tid":1544420,"uid":10079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T14:26:42.000Z","msg":"11<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/y7yRDOLCy4Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fy7yRDOLCy4Y&d=t4s0zgtGzRvDs5iH%2BzYNWAy1DEY80m5I9K8mtjxpzv8%3D&h=bbd6e293\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/y7yRDOLCy4Y</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/q4A00Xy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fq4A00Xy.jpg&h=74d43a3c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a7tRe1o.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa7tRe1o.png&h=432a4e32&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RA6rNta.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRA6rNta.jpg&h=9fe78eff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">毋忘所有義士之付出、612、721、805、811、824、825、831<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">打狗！救人！</span><br />\n無分和勇 團結抗暴<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n光復香港 時代革命</span>"},{"pid":"05e97c266124762a9132bd480484178a480e50c6","tid":1544420,"uid":63934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T14:27:05.000Z","msg":"蓋世太保?"},{"pid":"aebf9a66446146dbf33619651921aaa0e616cf2c","tid":1544420,"uid":230382,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T14:27:19.000Z","msg":"dklm，係咪痴L左線，究竟佢有咩痛腳比人捉住？定佢真心膠？"},{"pid":"c7855feb947bd04d370f6857c3a9f7ccf843ce55","tid":1544420,"uid":230382,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T14:27:55.000Z","msg":"負皮意思係支持？"},{"pid":"628aaef1d0ba947ad4860250b4a19b02f5e536c4","tid":1544420,"ui